text.49: De Murga: I think El Clasico is the biggest match in the world for clubs. It’s good to make a promotion of football in the Philippines to get people interested in football. There’s a lot of great players in each team, and it’s always a fun game to watch. https://t.co/SgGrtZmDsB
text.50: Marañon: The Clasico is the best game ever that you can watch around the world. There is no other game that can compare to them. Even if they don’t like football, if they watch El Clasico, they will enjoy and they will like football from there. https://t.co/SgGrtZmDsB

text.53: De Murga: I’ll have to go for Messi. How he dominated not just scoring goals, also just assisting. Even though all the great players who went through Barcelona and Real Madrid, I’d say Messi and Ronaldo help each other to become better. #RapplerTalk https://t.co/SgGrtZmDsB
text.54: Del Rosario: He’s always been so cool on the ball. But I just want to see being on the field with him because he makes everything look so much easier than it is…. That guy is just magic. #RapplerTalk https://t.co/SgGrtZmDsB
text.55: Del Rosario: When it comes down to players, one from Real Madrid that I’d probably choose would be Zidane. He’s one of the greatest players I’ve ever seen play. #RapplerTalk https://t.co/SgGrtZmDsB
text.56: Marañon: He was the best player of the world for many years. It’s amazing how he and Messi fight to be the best for how many years. #RapplerTalk https://t.co/SgGrtZmDsB
text.57:
“If you were to choose a player in the history of El Clasico, who will you import to play alongside with?”

Marañon: If I have to choose one, for me it’s Cristiano. #RapplerTalk https://t.co/SgGrtZmDsB
text.58: De Murga: On top of that, one of my favorite players of Barcelona is Andres Iniesta, which other things that they achieved together are not just in Barcelona but also for the national team. I cannot choose just one player. #RapplerTalk https://t.co/SgGrtZmDsB
text.59: De Murga: I cannot say also I have a favorite player out of all. To me I think that Messi is the GOAT. I’ve never seen people do what Messi does. He plays with professionals like he’s playing against kids. And you’ve never seen that kind of superiority in the history of football.
text.60: Marañon: I don’t really have a favorite. I like Cristiano because he gives Real Madrid too many things, not only goals. He makes the teams afraid when they play against Madrid, only because Cristiano was playing.
